title: For Rent - Downey Plaza Apartments
posting_body: ["At Downey Plaza Apartments in Downey, CA, you've discovered your new home.", 'This apartment community is located on Birchcrest Rd.', 'in Downey.', 'One Bedroom/One Bath Apartment for $1,500.00 with a 12 month lease.', 'The security deposit is $1,000.00 (On Approved Credit) and can apply with only $40.00 Per Adult! 😊', 'Utilities Included: Water and Trash.', 'Pet Policy: Pets Not Allowed.', 'Visit us on Instagram or <URL> to see pictures of our apartments.', '<URL>', 'NOTE: Due to COVID-19 Pandemic, our office is currently closed.', 'We are open by appointment only.', 'You may contact us via our telephone to schedule an appointment for a tour.', '•Built in 1961', '•90 Units/2 Stories', 'Apartment Amenities - Unique Features', '•Easy Access to the 5 & 605 Freeway', '•Gated Parking', '•Blinds', '•Patios', '•No Pets Allowed', '•1 space; Assigned Parking.', '•12 Month Lease', '•Laundry Facilities', '•Pool', '•Air Conditioning', '•Heating', '•Ceiling Fans', '•Smoke Free', '•Disposal', '•Gas Stove & Oven', '•Vinyl Flooring', '•Window Coverings', '•Outdoor Space', '•Patio', '•Controlled Access']
